{"id": "art-134", "label": "Art. 134", "title": "Art. 134", "slug": "art-134", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 134 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_746921769\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2273\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_746921769\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Ac&#355;ionarii</b></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'> care nu au votat în favoarea unei\nhot&#259;râri a adun&#259;rii generale au dreptul de a se retrage din societate\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de a solicita cump&#259;rarea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> lor de c&#259;tre societate, numai\ndac&#259; respectiva hot&#259;râre a adun&#259;rii generale are ca obiect:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1295694907\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2272\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1295694907\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)schimbarea obiectului principal de activitate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1317373512\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2271\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1317373512\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)transformarea transfrontalier&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1347634312\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2270\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1347634312\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)schimbarea formei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_539540171\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2269\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_539540171\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)fuziunea sau divizarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ninclusiv transfrontalier&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_32154541\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2268\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_32154541\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dreptul de retragere poate fi exercitat în termen de 30\nde zile de la data public&#259;rii hot&#259;rârii adun&#259;rii generale în\nMonitorul Oficial al României, Partea a IV-a, în cazurile prev&#259;zute la\nalin. (1) lit. a)-c), <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de la data\nadopt&#259;rii hot&#259;rârii adun&#259;rii generale, în cazul prev&#259;zut la\nalin. (1) lit. d).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1587389422\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2267\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1587389422\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)În cazul fuziunilor, transform&#259;rilor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> diviz&#259;rilor transfrontaliere, <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> care nu sunt în favoarea <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> pot exercita dreptul de retragere potrivit\nprevederilor art. 251<sup>30</sup>, art. 251<sup>49</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nart. 251<sup>69</sup>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_367663486\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2266\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_367663486\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> vor depune la\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, al&#259;turi de <span\nclass=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> scris&#259; de retragere, <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> pe care le posed&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz,\ncertificatele de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span> emise potrivit art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>97</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_392864280\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2265\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_392864280\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#355;ul</span> pl&#259;tit de\nsocietate pentru <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> celui care\nexercit&#259; dreptul de retragere va fi stabilit de un expert autorizat\nindependent, ca valoare medie ce rezult&#259; din aplicarea a cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; metode de evaluare recunoscute de <span\nclass=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> în vigoare la data evalu&#259;rii. Expertul\neste numit de registratorul de registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\nîn conformitate cu <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 38 <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 39, la cererea consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv a directoratului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1604414299\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2264\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1604414299\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Costurile de evaluare vor fi suportate de societate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}